title: Road to Avonlea. Season 2
description:
Season 2 of this enchanting canadian tv-series. Quality not perfect, but acceptable. 

Names of the episodes:

 1. Sara's homecoming
 2. How kissing was discovered
 3. Aunt Hetty's ordeal
 4. Of corsets, secrets and true true love
 5. Old quarrels, old love
 6. May the best man win
 7. Family rivalry
 8. Sea ghost
 9. All that glitters
10. Dreamer of dreams
11. It's just a stage
12. A mother's love
13. Misfits and miracles
